      "MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|40048,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|56946,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|2555,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|12574,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1597582",
